<h3 data-section-id="dyrp92" data-start="77" data-end="99">🔹 What Dontpad is</h3>
<ul data-start="100" data-end="285">
<li data-section-id="4ah6we" data-start="100" data-end="141">
<p data-start="102" data-end="141">It’s a <strong data-start="109" data-end="139">minimal online text editor</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="15s8faz" data-start="142" data-end="205">
<p data-start="144" data-end="205">You can <strong data-start="152" data-end="203">write and share text instantly using just a URL</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hc1oac" data-start="206" data-end="285">
<p data-start="208" data-end="285">No signup, no login, nothing required <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 52px;"><a href="https://dontpad.com/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://dontpad.com/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 52px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Dontpad</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1mjjf1v" data-start="287" data-end="319">🔹 How it works (super easy)</h3>
<ul data-start="320" data-end="498">
<li data-section-id="1405cjv" data-start="320" data-end="354">
<p data-start="322" data-end="354">You open: <code data-start="332" data-end="354">dontpad.com/anything</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="118hwq" data-start="355" data-end="395">
<p data-start="357" data-end="395">Example: <code data-start="366" data-end="395">dontpad.com/manikanta-notes</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wp2r2" data-start="396" data-end="441">
<p data-start="398" data-end="441">That page becomes your <strong data-start="421" data-end="441">personal notepad</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8xxn2j" data-start="442" data-end="498">
<p data-start="444" data-end="498">Anyone with the link can <strong data-start="469" data-end="498">view/edit it in real-time</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1lc6q8i" data-start="500" data-end="519">🔹 Key features</h3>
<ul data-start="520" data-end="846">
<li data-section-id="wm16w" data-start="520" data-end="602">
<p data-start="522" data-end="602">✍️ <strong data-start="525" data-end="538">Auto-save</strong> (no save button needed) <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 59px;"><a href="https://dontpad.en.uptodown.com/android?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://dontpad.en.uptodown.com/android?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 59px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Uptodown</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10kbpyy" data-start="603" data-end="637">
<p data-start="605" data-end="637">🔗 <strong data-start="608" data-end="635">Share by link instantly</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="4hjw5e" data-start="638" data-end="737">
<p data-start="640" data-end="737">👥 <strong data-start="643" data-end="670">Real-time collaboration</strong> (multiple people can edit) <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center select-none relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill" style="width: 59px;"><a href="https://dontpad.en.uptodown.com/android?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://dontpad.en.uptodown.com/android?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! select-none" style="max-width: 59px;"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">Uptodown</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="13s5jhq" data-start="738" data-end="806">
<p data-start="740" data-end="806">📂 You can create folders like:<br data-start="771" data-end="774">
<code data-start="776" data-end="804">dontpad.com/project1/notes</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19kzioh" data-start="807" data-end="846">
<p data-start="809" data-end="846">📥 Can download your text as a file</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="8wtcqz" data-start="848" data-end="873">🔹 When people use it</h3>
<ul data-start="874" data-end="1032">
<li data-section-id="10u0j5q" data-start="874" data-end="912">
<p data-start="876" data-end="912">Quick note sharing between friends</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="cmmlze" data-start="913" data-end="966">
<p data-start="915" data-end="966">Temporary text storage (like copying code, links)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="8tkdw" data-start="967" data-end="989">
<p data-start="969" data-end="989">Team brainstorming</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1emd6ra" data-start="990" data-end="1032">
<p data-start="992" data-end="1032">Sending text without creating accounts</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1034" data-end="1037">
<h3 data-section-id="u5nsit" data-start="1039" data-end="1063">⚠️ Important warning</h3>
<ul data-start="1064" data-end="1175">
<li data-section-id="1eh2joo" data-start="1064" data-end="1094">
<p data-start="1066" data-end="1094">❌ <strong data-start="1068" data-end="1094">No security or privacy</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="upv0ej" data-start="1095" data-end="1135">
<p data-start="1097" data-end="1135">❌ Anyone with the link can edit/delete</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="968mnb" data-start="1136" data-end="1175">
<p data-start="1138" data-end="1175">❌ Not for passwords or sensitive data</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1177" data-end="1180">
<p data-start="1182" data-end="1261">👉 In short:<br data-start="1194" data-end="1197">
<strong data-start="1197" data-end="1261">Dontpad = fastest way to share text online without any login</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1263" data-end="1266">
<p data-start="1268" data-end="1396">If you want, I can show you some <strong data-start="1301" data-end="1324">better alternatives</strong> (like Pastebin, Notion, etc.) depending on what you want to use it for.</p>
</div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center