<p data-start="3019" data-end="3024">Then:</p>
<ul data-start="3025" data-end="3071">
<li data-section-id="x36zfx" data-start="3025" data-end="3041">
<p data-start="3027" data-end="3041">Use WebSockets</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lxving" data-start="3042" data-end="3071">
<p data-start="3044" data-end="3071">Broadcast changes instantly</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3073" data-end="3125">If you want, I can give you <strong data-start="3101" data-end="3124">full real-time code</strong>.</p>
