<p data-start="3795" data-end="3850">Open same URL in another tab → <strong data-start="3826" data-end="3850">live sync working 🔥</strong></p>
<hr data-start="3852" data-end="3855">
<h1 data-section-id="1i7gje" data-start="3857" data-end="3890">🔥 What makes this “full clone”</h1>
<p data-start="3891" data-end="4012">✔ Real-time sync (Socket.IO)<br data-start="3919" data-end="3922">
✔ Multi-user editing<br data-start="3942" data-end="3945">
✔ Persistent storage<br data-start="3965" data-end="3968">
✔ Infinite documents via URL<br data-start="3996" data-end="3999">
✔ Auto-save</p>
<hr data-start="4014" data-end="4017">
<h1 data-section-id="1y7zctg" data-start="4019" data-end="4054">⚠️ What Dontpad still does better</h1>
<p data-start="4055" data-end="4071">Let’s be honest:</p>
<ul data-start="4072" data-end="4209">
<li data-section-id="trtci7" data-start="4072" data-end="4108">
<p data-start="4074" data-end="4108">Their infra is ultra-lightweight</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fcurxg" data-start="4109" data-end="4139">
<p data-start="4111" data-end="4139">Handles concurrency better</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="s5wvqv" data-start="4140" data-end="4209">
<p data-start="4142" data-end="4209">Probably uses optimized text diffing (not full replace like ours)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4211" data-end="4214">
<h1 data-section-id="1lp0zqb" data-start="4216" data-end="4269">🚀 If you want TRUE production-level (next upgrade)</h1>
<p data-start="4270" data-end="4289">I can help you add:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="77l1fw" data-start="4291" data-end="4315">💎 Advanced features</h3>
<ul data-start="4316" data-end="4522">
<li data-section-id="kkfd8" data-start="4316" data-end="4354">
<p data-start="4318" data-end="4354">Cursor positions (Google Docs style)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="qek9bc" data-start="4355" data-end="4414">
<p data-start="4357" data-end="4414">Operational Transform / CRDT (real collaborative editing)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1kuckrp" data-start="4415" data-end="4433">
<p data-start="4417" data-end="4433">Markdown preview</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="88ss90" data-start="4434" data-end="4461">
<p data-start="4436" data-end="4461">Access control (optional)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ltu6ci" data-start="4462" data-end="4488">
<p data-start="4464" data-end="4488">Rate limiting + security</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1rw6qcv" data-start="4489" data-end="4522">
<p data-start="4491" data-end="4522">Cloud deploy (Render / Railway)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4524" data-end="4527">
<h1 data-section-id="dk3fh7" data-start="4529" data-end="4551">💬 Tell me next step</h1>
<p data-start="4552" data-end="4569">Say one of these:</p>
