<li data-section-id="jm01ie" data-start="4570" data-end="4604">
<p data-start="4572" data-end="4604">👉 “make it Google Docs level”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1922o3h" data-start="4605" data-end="4628">
<p data-start="4607" data-end="4628">👉 “deploy it live”</p>
</li>
