<p data-start="1019" data-end="1053">Works same as Linux-style terminal</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1055" data-end="1058">
<h1 data-section-id="more2v" data-start="1060" data-end="1099">📱 If you’re ONLY on mobile (Android)</h1>
<p data-start="1100" data-end="1117">Then you can use:</p>
<ul data-start="1118" data-end="1157">
<li data-section-id="lyf7sl" data-start="1118" data-end="1157">
<p data-start="1120" data-end="1157"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Termux</span></span></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1159" data-end="1227">But honestly — building this project is <strong data-start="1199" data-end="1226">much easier on a laptop</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1229" data-end="1232">
<h1 data-section-id="kzre0k" data-start="1234" data-end="1259">🔥 Simple understanding</h1>
<p data-start="1260" data-end="1302">👉 “bash” = <strong data-start="1272" data-end="1302">just type this in terminal</strong></p>
<p data-start="1304" data-end="1384">Not a special software<br data-start="1326" data-end="1329">
Not a different language<br data-start="1353" data-end="1356">
Just a place to run commands</p>
<hr data-start="1386" data-end="1389">
