)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="e779d674-3fe6-405c-9e9e-be276b1c9286" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="209">Alright — if you’re stuck already, then building a full backend + MongoDB app right now is just going to frustrate you. Let’s switch to a <strong data-start="138" data-end="160">much easier method</strong> that still gives you a working Dontpad-like app.</p>
<p data-start="211" data-end="319">👉 No backend<br data-start="224" data-end="227">
👉 No installation headaches<br data-start="255" data-end="258">
👉 Works directly in browser<br data-start="286" data-end="289">
👉 You can deploy in minutes</p>
<hr data-start="321" data-end="324">
<h1 data-section-id="14fu18g" data-start="326" data-end="405">🚀 EASIEST WAY: Use <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Firebase</span></span> (No backend coding)</h1>
<p data-start="407" data-end="450">This is how beginners build real apps fast.</p>
<hr data-start="452" data-end="455">
<h1 data-section-id="1ln03wv" data-start="457" data-end="479">🧱 What you’ll build</h1>
<ul data-start="480" data-end="558">
<li data-section-id="1rkyor2" data-start="480" data-end="508">
<p data-start="482" data-end="508">Unique URL = unique note</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="3d9r63" data-start="509" data-end="522">
<p data-start="511" data-end="522">Auto-save</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="lt18q5" data-start="523" data-end="541">
<p data-start="525" data-end="541">Real-time sync</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10zawl1" data-start="542" data-end="558">
<p data-start="544" data-end="558">Works online</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="560" data-end="563">
<h1 data-section-id="t6826j" data-start="565" data-end="595">⚡ STEP-BY-STEP (VERY SIMPLE)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="58022t" data-start="597" data-end="633">✅ Step 1: Create Firebase project</h2>
<ol data-start="634" data-end="768">
<li data-section-id="x1o75q" data-start="634" data-end="681">
<p data-start="637" data-end="681">Go to: <a data-start="644" data-end="679" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://console.firebase.google.com/">https://console.firebase.google.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1spugo6" data-start="682" data-end="709">
<p data-start="685" data-end="709">Click <strong data-start="691" data-end="709">Create Project</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q8dosa" data-start="710" data-end="737">
<p data-start="713" data-end="737">Name it: <code data-start="722" data-end="737">dontpad-clone</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="9iiw29" data-start="738" data-end="768">
<p data-start="741" data-end="768">Click <strong data-start="747" data-end="768">Continue → Finish</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="770" data-end="773">
<h2 data-section-id="1l88g3i" data-start="775" data-end="803">✅ Step 2: Enable Database</h2>
<ol data-start="804" data-end="900">
<li data-section-id="1sf6009" data-start="804" data-end="860">
<p data-start="807" data-end="860">Inside project → Click <strong data-start="830" data-end="860">Build → Firestore Database</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ovwvee" data-start="861" data-end="889">
<p data-start="864" data-end="889">Click <strong data-start="870" data-end="889">Create Database</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16hyqxr" data-start="890" data-end="900">
<p data-start="893" data-end="900">Choose:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="901" data-end="939"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Start in test mode</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<ol start="4" data-start="940" data-end="967">
<li data-section-id="1rveluz" data-start="940" data-end="967">
<p data-start="943" data-end="967">Select any region → Done</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="969" data-end="972">
<h2 data-section-id="1vuk5fa" data-start="974" data-end="1002">✅ Step 3: Get your config</h2>
<ol data-start="1003" data-end="1112">
<li data-section-id="1oshulu" data-start="1003" data-end="1035">
<p data-start="1006" data-end="1035">Click <strong data-start="1012" data-end="1035">Project Settings ⚙️</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="gwkoro" data-start="1036" data-end="1059">
<p data-start="1039" data-end="1059">Scroll → “Your apps”</p>
</li>
