<hr data-start="145" data-end="148">
<h1 data-section-id="yytoii" data-start="150" data-end="186">✅ FIX IT STEP-BY-STEP (DON’T SKIP)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="18tm1pt" data-start="188" data-end="226">🔹 Step 1: Install Node.js properly</h2>
<ol data-start="228" data-end="382">
<li data-section-id="o6kwds" data-start="228" data-end="265">
<p data-start="231" data-end="265">Go here:<br data-start="239" data-end="242">
👉 <a data-start="245" data-end="263" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://nodejs.org/">https://nodejs.org<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
