<p data-start="57" data-end="184">👉 <strong data-start="60" data-end="89">“Cannot GET /test” means:</strong><br>
Your server is running, but it doesn’t know to show <code data-start="142" data-end="154">index.html</code> for custom URLs like <code data-start="176" data-end="183">/test</code>.</p>
<hr data-start="186" data-end="189">
<h1 data-section-id="9k85y6" data-start="191" data-end="223">✅ FIX (JUST ADD 1 SMALL THING)</h1>
