But I’ll be honest: adding <strong data-start="83" data-end="106">PDFs, images, files</strong> is NOT a small UI change — you need backend support for uploads.</p>
<p data-start="173" data-end="243">Don’t worry — I’ll give you the <strong data-start="205" data-end="242">simplest working way step-by-step</strong>.</p>
