 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼs">git</span><span> init</span><br><span class="ͼs">git</span><span> add .</span><br><span class="ͼs">git</span><span> commit </span><span class="ͼu">-m</span><span> </span><span class="ͼr">"first commit"</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="635" data-end="638">
<h2 data-section-id="1q4ecfd" data-start="640" data-end="667">🔹 Create repo on GitHub</h2>
<ol data-start="668" data-end="766">
<li data-section-id="110tzwy" data-start="668" data-end="697">
<p data-start="671" data-end="697">Go to <a data-start="677" data-end="695" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://github.com/">https://github.com<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
