<p data-start="153" data-end="172">Right now you have:</p>
<ul data-start="173" data-end="233">
<li data-section-id="bfri7e" data-start="173" data-end="193">
<p data-start="175" data-end="193">Upload + preview</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="105a6vq" data-start="194" data-end="213">
<p data-start="196" data-end="213">Persistent docs</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bdu7af" data-start="214" data-end="233">
<p data-start="216" data-end="233">Live deployment</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="235" data-end="311">That’s a <strong data-start="244" data-end="258">solid base</strong>. Now move toward making it feel like a real product.</p>
<hr data-start="313" data-end="316">
<h1 data-section-id="ayspvq" data-start="318" data-end="357">🚀 BEST NEXT UPGRADES (Pick one path)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1ppayw6" data-start="359" data-end="411">🔹 1. Make it feel like TiinyHost (sharing focus)</h2>
<p data-start="412" data-end="471">If your goal is like <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">TiinyHost</span></span>:</p>
<p data-start="473" data-end="480">👉 Add:</p>
<ul data-start="481" data-end="557">
<li data-section-id="8xhf0t" data-start="481" data-end="504">
<p data-start="483" data-end="504">Copy link button 📋</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="12m64xm" data-start="505" data-end="528">
<p data-start="507" data-end="528">Shareable file page</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="d14dwd" data-start="529" data-end="557">
<p data-start="531" data-end="557">File name + size display</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="1qmymvw" data-start="559" data-end="583">Example improvement:</h3>
<p data-start="584" data-end="597">After upload:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="598" data-end="670"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="relative"><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼk ͼy"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼt">navigator</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>clipboard</span><span class="ͼn">.</span><span>writeText(</span><span class="ͼt">fileUrl</span><span>);</span><br><span class="ͼt">alert</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼr">"Link copied!"</span><span>);</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="672" data-end="675">
<h2 data-section-id="4x3c01" data-start="677" data-end="732">🔹 2. Make it like Dontpad (real-time collaboration)</h2>
<p data-start="734" data-end="741">👉 Add:</p>
<ul data-start="742" data-end="806">
<li data-section-id="1y7ee9q" data-start="742" data-end="770">
<p data-start="744" data-end="770">Live typing (no refresh)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1r32y44" data-start="771" data-end="806">
<p data-start="773" data-end="806">Multiple users editing same doc</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="808" data-end="822">This requires:</p>
<ul data-start="823" data-end="847">
<li data-section-id="1b7caxu" data-start="823" data-end="847">
<p data-start="825" data-end="847">Socket.IO (WebSockets)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="849" data-end="900">This is the <strong data-start="861" data-end="888">most impressive upgrade</strong> you can do.</p>
<hr data-start="902" data-end="905">
<h2 data-section-id="165gs5k" data-start="907" data-end="960">🔹 3. Make it like LinkedIn-style app (UI + posts)</h2>
<p data-start="962" data-end="969">👉 Add:</p>
<ul data-start="970" data-end="1049">
