</li>
<li data-section-id="1v9l3cw" data-start="1013" data-end="1037">
<p data-start="1015" data-end="1037">Each upload = a post</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="kaws6u" data-start="1038" data-end="1049">
<p data-start="1040" data-end="1049">Feed UI</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1051" data-end="1054">
<h2 data-section-id="ils29m" data-start="1056" data-end="1106">🔹 4. Add user system (important for real apps)</h2>
