<hr data-start="82" data-end="85">
<div class="group relative clear-both my-4 w-full overflow-visible"><div id="writing-block-572a6cbb-9274-49bf-9ad9-16d831495dc9" class="relative w-full overflow-clip rounded-[24px] bg-token-bg-primary dark:bg-[#2a2a2a] shadow-[0px_4px_80px_rgba(0,0,0,0.02)]" data-writing-block="true" data-testid="writing-block-container"><div class="z-1 md:sticky top-(--sticky-padding-top)" data-testid="writing-block-header-sticky-container"><div class="bg-token-bg-primary flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-3 font-sans dark:bg-[#2a2a2a] py-2.5" data-testid="writing-block-header-surface" style="padding-left: calc(5 * var(--spacing)); padding-right: calc(1 * var(--spacing));"><div class="flex grow gap-3 items-center"><div class="text-token-text-tertiary flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 grow cursor-default items-center self-center text-sm font-medium"><div class="truncate">Writing</div></div></div><div class="flex shrink-0 items-center"><div class="flex items-center"><button class="gap-1 select-none text-sm font-medium text-token-text-primary hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary flex size-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full p-1.5 transition-colors disabled:opacity-40 disabled:hover:bg-transparent" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><div class="writing-block-editor markdown-new-styling relative flow-root pt-(--writing-block-editor-pt) pe-(--writing-block-editor-pr) pb-(--writing-block-editor-pb) ps-(--writing-block-editor-pl)" style="--writing-block-editor-pt: 0px; --writing-block-editor-pr: calc(5 * var(--spacing)); --writing-block-editor-pb: calc(4 * var(--spacing)); --writing-block-editor-pl: calc(5 * var(--spacing));"><div class="ProseMirror markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full min-h-6 break-words focus:outline-none" contenteditable="true" aria-disabled="false" dir="auto" translate="no"><p><span>I recently built a lightweight file sharing and note-taking web application inspired by tools like TiinyHost and Dontpad.</span></p><p><span>The goal was to create a simple platform where users can upload files, generate shareable links, and manage content in a clean interface without unnecessary complexity.</span></p><p><span>Key features include:</span></p><ul data-spread="false"><li><p><span>File upload and preview (images, PDFs, and more)</span></p></li><li><p><span>Persistent document storage</span></p></li><li><p><span>Shareable access through unique URLs</span></p></li><li><p><span>Clean and responsive UI inspired by LinkedIn and Instagram layouts</span></p></li></ul><p><span>During development, I worked with Node.js, Express, and frontend technologies to handle file management, data persistence, and deployment.</span></p><p><span>This project helped me understand full-stack development concepts such as file handling, API design, and deploying applications for real-world usage.</span></p><p><span>Looking forward to enhancing it further by adding real-time collaboration, user authentication, and cloud storage.</span></p><p><span>Feedback and suggestions are welcome.</span></p></div></div><div aria-hidden="true" class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 z-2 rounded-[24px] shadow-[inset_0px_0px_0px_1px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07)]"></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="1087" data-end="1090">
<p data-start="1092" data-end="1116">If you want, I can also:</p>
<ul data-start="1117" data-end="1235">
<li data-section-id="vdz684" data-start="1117" data-end="1162">
<p data-start="1119" data-end="1162">Make it sound more <strong data-start="1138" data-end="1162">impressive/technical</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ej3aej" data-start="1163" data-end="1187">
<p data-start="1165" data-end="1187">Add <strong data-start="1169" data-end="1187">your teammates</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1fpjkjk" data-start="1188" data-end="1235">
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1235">Or tailor it for <strong data-start="1207" data-end="1235">recruiters / internships</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1237" data-end="1252" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Just tell me 👍</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-df3050c8.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false"