0rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="0213db10-1388-4118-8b5f-9081a1edbd29" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-3" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word dark markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="193">Short answer: <strong data-start="14" data-end="96">you can try Google AdSense, but your current app likely won’t get approved yet</strong>. Not because it’s bad—because AdSense has strict requirements beyond just having a working site.</p>
<p data-start="195" data-end="225">Let’s break it down clearly 👇</p>
<hr data-start="227" data-end="230">
<h1 data-section-id="od7uzb" data-start="232" data-end="282">💡 What is <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Google AdSense</span></span></h1>
<ul data-start="283" data-end="374">
<li data-section-id="1jvrtxh" data-start="283" data-end="312">
<p data-start="285" data-end="312">Shows ads on your website</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10swp9k" data-start="313" data-end="346">
<p data-start="315" data-end="346">You earn money per click/view</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="44wnxn" data-start="347" data-end="374">
<p data-start="349" data-end="374">Requires approval first</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="376" data-end="379">
<h1 data-section-id="dkniyw" data-start="381" data-end="424">🚫 Why your current site may get rejected</h1>
<p data-start="426" data-end="445">Right now your app:</p>
<ul data-start="446" data-end="550">
<li data-section-id="1dut1km" data-start="446" data-end="484">
<p data-start="448" data-end="484">Mostly tool-based (upload + notes)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="mjlzoa" data-start="485" data-end="506">
<p data-start="487" data-end="506">Low content/pages</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1pe5lqi" data-start="507" data-end="525">
<p data-start="509" data-end="525">No legal pages</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="kt7how" data-start="526" data-end="550">
<p data-start="528" data-end="550">Possibly low traffic</p>
</li>
</ul>
