<h2 data-section-id="dp3xwa" data-start="602" data-end="647">🔹 STEP 3: Open correctly (VERY IMPORTANT)</h2>
<p data-start="649" data-end="716">👉 DO NOT double-click HTML files<br data-start="682" data-end="685">
